## Completion rule

Do not claim Stage 3 complete unless:
- stage-3 scope is implemented,
- stage-3 mapping-reference-derived scenarios were covered,
- processor-backed session-interaction tests pass,
- stage-1 and stage-2 verification still pass,
- docs are updated.
